25485409.review:
My first review ever on Steam but this game totally deserves it! 

Onward is super immersing military sim we all have been waiting for. It's fun, co-operative and intense. Go buy it and support Dante, a sole developer working on it. 

Yes, there are bugs and movement feels a bit clunky but hey, for early access game this is gold. It seems he might be defining some crucial and critial concepts for VR FPS genre. I believe in a matter of 6 months, this game will be gold. 

Updates recommendations:
- Make "waiting room" more user friendly;
- Smoothen up the  in-game walk movement;
- Add another map or two for more variety (office interior, forest, an island maybe);
- Create Leaderboards for additional competitivness;
- Fix bugs.

Good luck and thanks for this experince and hard work!
